---
title: Pineapple-Apricot Pork Chops and Chicken Breast with Rosemary-Parmesan Potatoes and Snap Peas
description: Fresh pineapple and apricot spread make for the perfect sweet and savoury sauce to go with pork chops and chicken! A side of potatoes is finished with rosemary and a sprinkle of Parmesan for maximum flavour.
